    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sakura, The Jirai-kei Magical Girl》是一款具有选择项的小说游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孤身一人的主人公秋叶创志，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天在繁华的闹区街头，遇见了一个穿着地雷系服装的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她站在夕阳下，看起来又饿又无助，于心不忍的创志便给她买了些食物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没想到就在那之后，创志突然被一种名为“非人族”的危险存在袭击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >眼看就要命丧当场时，一名身穿赛博朋克风战斗服装的樱花发色少女出现在他面前，挡住了攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“——魔装启动。变身（Trance）！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——这是一场在守护变身少女战斗的同时，守护世界安宁的浪漫物语——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶小樱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV：藤崎 纱矢香</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“洗澡不是每天都要洗的。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras/68e5b5bfc1dbd3ecd7b9473e76555041.avif?t=1737705640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras_big/68e5b5bfc1dbd3ecd7b9473e76555041.avif?t=1737705640 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >国家秘密组织“超常灾害对策室”的行动队员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不谙世事，极度嫌麻烦，怕生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为除了战斗以外一个人什么都做不了，所以需要照顾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了战斗外，生活中什么事都做不好，所以需要别人照顾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且，她的食量惊人，每月的伙食费高达一百万日元。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶椿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV：みたかりん</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你可以认为我们的对策室是专门负责『UMA』的治安组织。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras/010a536886023ed60cb068e399297931.avif?t=1737705640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras_big/010a536886023ed60cb068e399297931.avif?t=1737705640 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超常灾害对策室的室长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几乎不离开本部。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是一位稳重且温柔的女性领导者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶秋叶 创志</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某次意外中成为小樱的专属「监护人」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天生热心肠，对需要帮助的人无法袖手旁观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用E-mote技术打造流畅的角色动画</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多条分支路线结局（ED）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美剧情CG </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Staff</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色设计：おやずり</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧本：あま味かぼちゃ</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作人：しながわ二郎</p></li></ul>",
